    "title": "Senior Fleet Manager at Wabash National India",
    "description": "Grow your career with Wabash National India! We are hiring a Fleet Manager for our Lucknow team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Wabash National India:\nWabash National India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wabash National India!",
